Class DataInitializer

java.lang.Object
model.DataInitializer
public class DataInitializer extends Object
The DataInitializer class is responsible for loading patient and staff details, as well as medical records from CSV files into their respective data structures. It also provides functionality to link medical records to patients.

    • linkMedicalRecordsToPatients

      Links medical records to their corresponding patients in the user map.
      Parameters:
      userMap - A map of users where the key is the user ID and the value is the User object.
